OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,FArtist Margo in Margate has said she
OL,7,Fhopes her new gallery show helps "make
OL,8,Fwomen visible" and contradict
OL,9,Fmisogynist narratives of influencers
OL,10,Fsuch as Andrew Tate.
OL,12,FThe former teacher, real name Margo
OL,13,FMcDaid, left the London primary school
OL,14,Fshe worked at in 2006 after one of her
OL,15,Fpupils and her mother was murdered by
OL,16,Fthe mother's boyfriend.
OL,18,FMcDaid said the incident left her
OL,19,F"ill" and "broken" and she still
OL,20,Fthinks about the little girl "every
OL,21,Fsingle day."
OL,26,@oD@bOUpD@NO]{D@AOU{D@EO]{D@KOU{D@RO]|D@
OL,26,A^OU}D@LO]
