FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,FShe credits painting with helping her
OL,7,Fheal, and also express her passion for
OL,8,Fadvocating for women.
OL,10,FHer new show of all-female paintings,
OL,11,FSisters With Secrets, has opened at
OL,12,FThe Pie Factory gallery in Margate,
OL,13,Fhelping to raise funds for domestic
OL,14,Fviolence services.
OL,16,F"It's really a nod to the fact that
OL,17,Flots of women do have secrets, and you
OL,18,Fdon't realise what women endure and
OL,19,Fexperience, but they turn up and
OL,20,Fthey're brilliant and they're bright
OL,21,Fand they're funny," she said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,F"Behind that is all these layers of
OL,7,Fwhat women experience, which is not
OL,8,Fobvious. Domestic violence is a
OL,9,Fmassive issue, and you meet women and
OL,10,Fthey're traumatised, but they still
OL,11,Fhave this vibrancy about them, and
OL,12,Fthat's what I'm trying to capture in
OL,13,Fmy work, that vibrant energy that
OL,14,Fwomen bring."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,FShe continued: "I worked as a teacher
OL,7,Fin King's Cross for ten years, and in
OL,8,Fthat part of London, we had a huge
OL,9,Fbunch of children who were really
OL,10,Fvulnerable. There was a Women's Refuge
OL,11,Faround the corner, and so we took
OL,12,Fchildren from that refuge.
OL,14,F"So we were working all the time with
OL,15,Fvulnerable kids, but also it was their
OL,16,Fmothers.
OL,18,F"These women who suffered a huge
OL,19,Ftrauma and abuse, and they still carry
OL,20,Fon.
OL,26,@nD@POUvD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,F"I was really, really ill after that
OL,7,Flittle girl died, and I just felt so
OL,8,Fbroken. And painting is my way of
OL,9,Fhealing."
OL,11,FShe continued: "I knew this little
OL,12,Fgirl. I knew she was vulnerable. The
OL,13,Fschool knew she was vulnerable.
OL,15,F"I was in a really good school, and
OL,16,Fthe ethos of the school was loving,
OL,17,Fcaring, brilliant energy, and
OL,18,Feverything that the school could have
OL,19,Fdone was was spot on, they got
OL,20,Feverything right in that case. But it
OL,21,Fwasn't enough.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@IO]sD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,F"A really violent man (killed them)
OL,7,Fand it was just horrific. And I still
OL,8,Fget upset about that, because how
OL,9,Fcould you not? How is this still
OL,10,Fhappening? Why is it still happening?"
OL,12,FDiscussing how painting has helped her
OL,13,Frecover from the horror of what
OL,14,Fhappened to her pupil and her mother,
OL,15,FMcDaid said: "I'm a woman, and I
OL,16,Fdefend the rights of women and and I
OL,17,Fthink in a world of Andrew Tates, you
OL,18,Fneed bright, beautiful women to
OL,19,Fcontradict that and show that we can
OL,20,Ftake up space."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]wD@NOU|D@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,FShe added: "I've had men come in and
OL,7,Fbe abusive about my art. One man came
OL,8,Finto the gallery and he said: "Why are
OL,9,Fnone of their mouths open?"
OL,11,F"Why would their mouth be open? Why
OL,12,Fwould you want women to have their
OL,13,Fmouth open in a painting? You don't
OL,14,Fget to come in and tell me what I
OL,15,Fshould be painting or what they should
OL,16,Flook like.
OL,26,@nD@LOUpD@_OUqD@[O]sD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,F"Making women visible is really
OL,7,Fimportant. And when people say to me:
OL,8,F'Why do you only paint women?' I
OL,9,Fthink: 'Why not? Why not just paint
OL,10,Fwomen?'
OL,12,F"If I was a landscape artist and I
OL,13,Fpainted mountains nobody would ever
OL,14,Fsay: 'Why just paint mountains?'"
OL,16,FShe continued: "That man that walked
OL,17,Fpast the gallery said: "Why are their
OL,18,Fmouths not open?" ` it's all part of
OL,19,Fit, all part of the system that thinks
OL,20,Fwomen should be there to do what? To
OL,21,Ffacilitate a world for men.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@aO]xD@POUyD@XOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1776517870
OL,3,CTeacher whose pupil was murdered opens
OL,4,Cgallery to 'make women visible'
OL,6,F"In my heart, I think about her (the
OL,7,Flittle girl at school) every single
OL,8,Fday and when I'm painting, because her
OL,9,Fmum was a really happy, beautiful,
OL,10,Fdancing, gorgeous woman. They were
OL,11,Fgenuinely really happy people.
OL,13,F"She shared happiness and it does
OL,14,Finspire my work, as my work is about
OL,15,Fmy love for life."
OL,17,FSisters With Secrets is at The Pie
OL,18,FFactory in Margate until April 20.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
